news.title: Repco Home Finance's net profit up 14.51% in Q2 FY25
news.para: Repco Home Finance's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 424.19 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 11.41 per cent from Rs 380.75 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Sunteck Realty posts net profit of Rs 34.62 crore in Q2 FY25
news.para: Sunteck Realty's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 182.05 crore in Q2 FY25 as against Rs 36.22 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Build Nivesh raises Rs 40 crore in maiden real estate AIF
news.para: "The fund has marked its final close with a total corpus of Rs 40 crore along with commitments of Rs 40 crore from its investors for add-on investment opportunities thereby augmenting the total investible corpus," it said.

news.title: Eldeco Housing & Industries' net profit dips 29.64% in Q2 FY25
news.para: Eldeco Housing & Industries' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 36.38 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 95.07 per cent from Rs 18.65 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Kochi: Residents of Chander Kunj Army towers approach HC over irregularities in construction
news.para: Earlier, Indian Institute of Science Bengaluru (IISc), which carried out a review and structural assessment as per a Kerala high court order, recommended the demolition of the twin towers in the AWHO housing complex.

news.title: Shalimar Paints posts net loss of Rs 19.62 crore in Q2 FY25
news.para: Shalimar Paints' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 146.13 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 20.15 per cent from Rs 121.62 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Segro to buy six Tritax EuroBox properties for $499 million in deal with Brookfield
news.para: Segro's purchase comes weeks after the Canadian asset manager outbid the London-based warehousing specialist in the race to buy Tritax EuroBox in a 1.1 billion pound ($1.41 billion) deal, including debt.

news.title: Rajasthan government plans to develop hi-tech city near Jaipur
news.para: Recently, Boston Consulting Group – a multinational consulting firm – gave a presentation on the concept of hi-tech cities, follwing which the state govt has started looking for suitable land on outskirts of Jaipur.

news.title: China planning to cut taxes on home buying: Report
news.para: China is looking to slash taxes on home purchases as the government strengthens fiscal support for its ailing real estate sector, a media report said on Tuesday.  Beijing has in recent months also announced a raft of measures aimed at boosting economic activity, including rate cuts and the easing of some home purchasing restrictions.

news.title: Industrial Investment Trust to launch Rs 500 crore AIF focused on real estate
news.para: The new AIF will focus on tier 1 and tier 2 cities. As on September 30, 2024, IITL's investment portfolio stands at Rs 405 crore.

news.title: Kolhapur: Focus back on merger of fringe areas into municipal limits
news.para: Shiv Sena candidate and former MLA Rajesh Kshirsagar has vowed to carry out the merger and thereby expand the city limits if the Mahayuti forms the govt after the election.

news.title: Kolte Patil Developers posts net profit of Rs 10.34 crore in Q2 FY25
news.para: Kolte Patil Developers' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 320.96 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 56.67 per cent from Rs 204.86 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Telangana govt to merge 24 municipalities into GHMC for greater city corporation plan
news.para: Sources said the merger of surrounding municipalities and villages with ORR would cover about 1,800 square km to 2,000 square km. As of now, the GHMC area is about 650 square km.

news.title: Bengaluru civic body to seal commercial properties over unpaid tax dues
news.para: Assistant revenue officers in each zone have been instructed to hold area-specific meetings to identify cases with substantial unpaid property taxes and ensure strict measures are taken for prompt collection.

news.title: Finolex Cables' net profit dips 23.85% in Q2 FY25
news.para: Finolex Cables' net consolidated total income stood at Rs 1,363.31 crore in Q2 FY25, a growth of 10.90 per cent from Rs 1,229.27 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Kalaignar Kanavu Illam scheme beneficiaries protest in Nilgiris
news.para: Kalaignar Kanavu Illam scheme beneficiaries demanded the release of the first instalment of the sanctioned amount for house construction under the scheme.

news.title: Mysuru: ED to investigate alternative and incentive schemes in Muda's 50:50 site scam
news.para: The urban development body offers incentive sites to farmers/ landowners who provide their land for development. However, Muda should have made deductions from compensation payments towards providing these incentive sites.

news.title: ED restitutes illegally sold Chennai land worth Rs 12 crore to rightful owner
news.para: The action was taken under the Prevention of Money Laundering Act (PMLA) after it lodged a criminal case against the accused on the basis of an FIR filed by the central crime branch (CCB) of Chennai Police, the federal agency said in a statement.

news.title: Bengaluru civic body collects 70% of property tax target by November 9
news.para: Mahadevapura zone has topped during 2024-25, contributing Rs 974 crore — or 74.4% — of the targeted Rs 1,309 crore.

news.title: Lucknow development body opens e-auction portal to sell its 300 properties
news.para: The portal was opened following the directives of Vice Chairman Prathamesh Kumar. It will remain open for online registration until Dec 11, with the e-auction scheduled for Dec 16.
